The Blood Angels were decimated in the Baal sector and now Lemartes and Astorath have gathered the remaining Chaplains to lead the Death Company to reclaim a hive city recently fallen to the Tyranids. The Tyranids have consumed all the biomass in the city and welcome more for their consumption. The mission is Purge the Foe and this will be an absolute blood bath!
